<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Registration</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <h3>Registration Confirmed!!</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>Hey {{name}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering for the event <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>. 
            We are excited to have you join us.
            </p>
            <p>When and where? {{eventDate}} | <a href="{{eventLink}}">Join Meeting</a></p>
            <p>Thank you once again for registering for the event. We look forward to seeing you there.</p>
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p>Event Management Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>